Subset liquor licenses

unique(liquor$STATUS)
liquor <- subset(liquor, STATUS == "Active" |
                   STATUS == "Issued")

unique(liquor$TYPE)
liquor2<- liquor %>%
  subset(TYPE == "Club"  |
           TYPE == "Nightclub"  |
           TYPE == "Tavern"  |
           TYPE == "Arena")
           
liquor2[!is.na(liquor2$LONGITUDE),]
liquor2[!is.na(liquor2$LATITUDE),]  

liquor <- liquor2
